%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Red%20Sea%20turmoil%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20keeping%20oil%20prices%20as%20high%20as%20they%20are%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225128%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oil%20rig%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bc058843bb77284ba2c3ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222564%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EFreddyTb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Red%20Sea%20tumult%20is%20raising%20the%20floor%20on%20oil%20prices%2C%20which%20would%20be%20lower%20absent%20the%20shipping%20disruptions%2C%20experts%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWeakness%20in%20the%20market%20from%20China's%20slowdown%20and%20questions%20around%20OPEC's%20strategy%20are%20keeping%20prices%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWithout%20the%20geopolitical%20chaos%2C%20US%20crude%20would%20be%20trading%20at%20%2470%20a%20barrel%2C%20about%202%25%20lower%20than%20levels%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attacks%20on%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20are%20a%20big%20geopolitical%20headache%2C%20and%20an%20economic%20one%2C%20too%2C%20as%20the%20chaos%20bleeds%20into%20markets%20by%20disrupting%20shipping%20flows%20and%20stoking%20inflationary%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20aren't%20oil%20prices%20reflecting%20the%20tension%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20is%3A%20they%20are%2C%20and%20the%20Red%20Sea%20attacks%20by%20Houthi%20militants%20are%20the%20only%20reason%20crude%20is%20trading%20as%20high%20as%20it%20is%2C%20experts%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20disruptions%20is%20hard%20to%20discern%20because%20of%20all%20the%20forces%20pulling%20oil%20prices%20down%2C%20analysts%20say%2C%20and%20oil%20would%20otherwise%20be%20trading%20much%20lower%20otherwise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Middle%20East%20angst%20wasn't%20a%20concern%20for%20markets%2C%20crude%20oil%20prices%20would%20be%20trading%20at%20around%20%2470-%2475%20a%20barrel%2C%20analysts%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20Western%20Texas%20Intermediate%20crude%20was%20at%20%2477%20a%20barrel.%20(Prices%20have%20since%20tumbled%20to%20%2472%20after%20an%20inaccurate%20Al-Jazeera%20headline%20about%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20it's%20going%20a%20lot%20higher%2C%20it's%20supporting%20the%20downside%20of%20what%20is%20looking%20like%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20fundamental%20weakness%2C%26quot%3B%20oil%20analyst%20Rebecca%20Babin%2C%20from%20CIBC%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20weakness%20stems%20from%20slowing%20demand%20in%20China%20and%20a%20surplus%20of%20oil%20in%20the%20market%20as%20non-OPEC%20nations%20keep%20pumping%20more%20crude.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20economy%20has%20seen%20sluggish%20economic%20growth%20post-COVID%2C%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-outlook-2024-beijing-investors-real-estate-property-markets-2023-12%5C%22%3Ekeep%20struggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20its%20real%20estate%20crisis%20continues%20and%20foreign%20investment%20in%20the%20economy%20dries%20up.%20Babin%20previously%20said%20that%20lackluster%20demand%20from%20the%20world's%20top%20oil%20importer%20will%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-market-outlook-2024-crude-prices-opec-china-us-production-2023-12%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20threat%20facing%20oil%20markets%20in%202024.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOPEC%20itself%20is%20another%20force%20pulling%20oil%20prices%20lower%20as%20the%20cartel%20has%20mostly%20%3Ca%20data-uri%3D%5C%22a7c5373fd451e9159f3d31aa607d2e6d%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-outlook-market-opec-cuts-crude-prices-us-production-boom-2023-12%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20data-analytics-