prices%20have%20rallied%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20seeing%20a%20million%20barrels%20a%20day%20of%20exports%20offline.%20So%20I%20think%20that's%20why%20it's%20been%20largely%20muted%20so%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%2C%20the%20international%20benchmark%20for%20prices%2C%20would%20be%20trading%20for%20lower%20per%20barrel%20without%20the%20geopolitical%20chaos%2C%20Kornfeind%20explained%20(about%20%2470%20to%20%2475%20a%20barrel%20when%20prices%20were%20at%20%2482%20a%20barrel%20on%20Wednesday).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20else%20equal%20(China's%20slowdown%2C%20OPEC%20concerns%2C%20and%20other%20fundamental%20pressures)%2C%20if%20a%20cease-fire%20isn't%20reached%2C%20Babin%20said%20prices%20of%20Brent%20crude%20could%20go%20up%20to%20%2490%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-outlook-opec-china-red-sea-shipping-crude-supply-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706967961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bc05b47a3d27148876d9f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price-outlook-opec-china-red-sea-shipping-crude-supply-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Red%20Sea%20chaos%20is%20actually%20creating%20a%20floor%20beneath%20prices%2C%20which%20would%20otherwise%20be%20dragged%20down%20by%20China's%20slowdown%20and%20other%20factors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price-outlook-opec-china-red-sea-shipping-crude-supply-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Temple%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20Now%20%E2%80%98King%E2%80%99s%20Court%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20Was%20Interrupted%20by%2