liament%E2%80%99s%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Birla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20then%20said%20that%20he%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20parliamentary%20system%20in%20the%20country%20under%20the%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20comes%20to%20the%20house%2C%20he%20is%20greeted%20with%20slogans.%20The%20responsibility%20with%20which%20we%20come%20to%20parliament%20has%20been%20forgotten.%20And%20the%20maharaja%20also%20comes%20and%20leaves%20without%20taking%20a%20single%20question%20from%20any%20department%20of%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBirla%20interrupted%20him%20again%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20motion%20of%20thanks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20talking%20about%20the%20history%20of%20this%20house.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20prime%20ministers%20and%20all%20have%20abided%20by%20their%20responsibilities%20by%20answering%20questions.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20maharaja%20who%20has%20not%20answered%20a%20single%20question%20of%20any%20department%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20may%20be%20his%20personal%20desire%20to%20convert%20India%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20into%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Erajtantra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bmonarchy%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20amid%20protests%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%20and%20Birla.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20then%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cevent%20management%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cattention%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20has%20a%20doctorate%20in%20event%20management.%20They%20have%20a%20PhD%20in%20attention%20management.%20When%20we%20ask%20why%20the%20prime%20minister%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20Manipur%2C%20they%20say%20look%20at%20the%20G20%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%20in%20Paris.%20When%20we%20say%20100%20people%20died%20during%20demonetisation%2C%20they%20say%20look%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20face%20on%20Paytm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20raise%20questions%20on%20China%20entering%20our%20territory%2C%20they%20try%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20by%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%98we%20are%20more%20powerful%20than%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99.%20When%20we%20say%20coal%20mines%20have%20been%20given%20to%20Adani%2C%20they%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frestoration-of-rahul-gandhis-lok-sabha-members-is-a-rebuke-to-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspend%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20farmers%20die%20by%20suicide%2C%20youth%20say%20they%20are%20unemployed%2C%20women%20say%20that%20there%20is%20inflation%2C%20when%2010%25%20of%20the%20population%20is%20controlling%2050%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20wealth%2C%20they%20claim%20to%20be%20the%20fastest-growing%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20use%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Blies%5D%20to%20hide%20their%20failures%20to%20weaken%20democracy.%20They%20want%20to%20trap%20people%20in%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20mayajaal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bnet%20of%20illusion%5D%20to%20make%20the%20king%20more%20powerful%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20added%20that%20while%20he%20respects%20the%20humble%20beginnings%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20he%20has%20lost%20touch%20with%20the%20common%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20sad%20part%20is%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20his%20chair%20to%20such%20a%20height%20that%20he%20c