ery%20high%20volumes%20Ramsay%20said.%20It%20gives%20incentives%20for%20a%20trading%20firm%20to%20trade%20stocks%20that%20provide%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20bang%20for%20the%20buck%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20results%20in%20better%20pricing%20for%20the%20firm's%20other%20trades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20has%20proposed%20to%20restrict%20this%20practice%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20creates%20an%20anti-competitive%20environment.%20The%20argument%20is%20that%20eliminating%20rebate%20tiers%20would%20do%20away%20with%20exchange%20inefficiencies%2C%20as%20capital%20flows%20wouldn't%20reward%20stocks%20that%20game%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20volumes%20also%20give%20sub-dollar%20stocks%20a%20false%20of%20sense%20of%20attraction%20among%20retail%20investors.%20It's%20problematic%20as%20these%20assets%20are%20already%20known%20for%20volatility%20and%20high-risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHigh%20trading%20volume%20influenced%20by%20factors%20other%20than%20the%20fundamental%20value%20of%20listed%20companies%20can%20absolutely%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20substantial%20losses%20to%20investors%20who%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20discern%20the%20reasons%20for%20that%20higher%20volume%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramsay%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20Jefferies%20notes%20a%20similar%20dynamic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStocks%20around%20%241%2Fshare%20have%20become%20popular%20with%20retail%20investors%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20so%20one%20might%20reasonably%20ask%20whether%20they%20are%20foregoing%20investments%20in%20other%20names%20%E2%80%93%20e.g.%2C%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20%E2%80%93%20and%20opting%20for%20sub-%241%20stocks%20instead.%20And%20if%20so%2C%20how%20might%20that%20impact%20liquidity%20in%20other%20more%20traditional%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20doesn't%20help%20that%20these%20assets%20remain%20included%20on%20indices%2C%20as%20it%20provides%20them%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbadge%20of%20legitimacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramsay%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Nasdaq%20requires%20firms%20meet%20a%20%241.00%20threshold%20for%20their%20shares%20to%20continue%20trading%2C%20companies%20below%20that%20level%20are%20given%20a%20180-day%20grace%20period%20to%20conform.%20It's%20led%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20reverse%20stock%20splits%2C%20a%20move%20where%20a%20company%20decreases%20its%20share%20count%20to%20boost%20the%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E255%20such%20splits%20occurred%20in%202023%2C%20compared%20to%20159%20the%20year%20before%2C%20Jefferies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20lackluster%20U.S.%20IPO%20market%2C%20it's%20quite%20reasonable%20to%20see%20how%20exchanges%20would%20want%20to%20help%20companies%20remain%20publicly%20listed%2C%26quot%3B%20Jefferies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpenny-stocks-spac-ipo-boom-risk-trade-volumes-nasdaq-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706967062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fadc1cd1e8d500019813462%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fpenny-stocks-spac-ipo-boom-risk-trade-volumes-nasdaq-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20are%20now%20hundreds%20of%20US-listed%20stocks%20trading%20below%20a%20dollar.%20It's%20creating%20market%20inefficiencies%2C%20IEX's%20John%20Ramsay%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fpenny-stocks-spac-ipo-boom-risk-trade-volumes-nasdaq-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Michael%20Jordan's%20championship%20sneakers%20sold%20for%20a%20record-breaking%20%248m%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5