3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market's%20bull%20case%20just%20got%20stronger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22happy%20trader%20nyse%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fa00b106f5b310011724bb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222953%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENed%20Davis%20Research%20forecasts%20more%20upside%20ahead%20for%20stocks.%3Cp%3EDrew%20Angerer%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere's%20more%20evidence%20that%20stocks%20are%20in%20a%20secular%20bull%20cycle%2C%20Ned%20Davis%20Research%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEquities'%20recent%20performance%2C%20among%20other%20economic%20indicators%2C%20suggests%20more%20upside%20ahead.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESince%20hitting%20its%20secular%20bottom%20in%202009%2C%20the%20Dow%20has%20hit%20fresh%20all-time%20highs%20every%20year%20for%2012%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20coming%20off%20a%20banner%20year%20in%20the%20US%20stock%20market%20%E2%80%94%20and%20there%20could%20be%20plenty%20more%20gains%20ahead%2C%20according%20to%20Ned%20Davis%20Research.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20published%20Thursday%2C%20chief%20global%20investment%20strategist%20Tim%20Hayes%20highlighted%20a%20handful%20of%20fresh%20evidence%20that%20suggests%20a%20secular%2C%20long-term%20bull%20cycle%20is%20indeed%20still%20alive%20and%20well.%20The%20recent%20strength%20in%20equities%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20thesis%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-us-gdp-inflation-federal-reserve-economic-growth-canada-germany-2024-1%5C%22%3Ebroader%20macroeconomic%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20support%20forecasts%20for%20more%20gains%20to%20come.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20months%2C%20stocks%20have%20passed%20what%20Hayes%20called%20the%20duck%20test%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20duck%2C%20swims%20like%20a%20duck%2C%20and%20quacks%20like%20a%20duck%2C%20then%20it%20probably%20is%20a%20duck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dow%20Jones%20Industrial%20Average%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20notched%20record%20highs%20already%20this%20year%2C%20which%20have%20been%20followed%20by%20records%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20Since%20the%20Dow%20hit%20its%20secular%20bottom%20in%202009%2C%20it's%20advanced%20with%20higher%20highs%20and%20higher%20lows%2C%20touching%20fresh%20all-time%20highs%20every%20year%20for%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tracks%20the%20trend%20seen%20in%20the%20secular%20bull%20cycles%20of%20the%20last%20100%20years%2C%20according%20to%20NDR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221352%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Secular%20bull%20markets%20of%20the%20last%20century%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd39937a3d271488773f26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221169%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20last%20century%20of%20secular%20bulls%20are%20highlighted%20in%20green.%3Cp%3ENDR%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20absolute%20performance%20has%20been%20strong%2C%20so%20have%20the%20measures%20of%20relative%20performance%2C%20Hayes%20added.%20Stocks%20tend%20to%20outperform%20bonds%20and%20commodities%20during%20secular%20bull%20cycles%2C%20as%20they%20are%20today%2C%20and%20that%20provides%20further%20%26quot%3Bsecular%20confirmation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecular%20bull%20markets%20also%20tend%20to%20result%20in%20US%20outperformance%20compared%20to%20other%20regions'%20stock%20markets%2C%20the%20strategist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20low%20unemployment%2C%20rising%20confidence%2C%20and%20strong%20GDP%20figures%20also%20imply%20a%20positive%20macro%20picture%2C%20which%20together%20support%20a%20secular%20bull%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20point%2C%20labor%20market%20data%20out%20Friday%20showed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b