usinessinsider.com%2Ffamily-vacation-mother-daughter-bonding-time-with-twin-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Italy%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20come%20in%20handy%20for%20keeping%20our%20active%20toddler%20entertained%20on%20the%20flight.%20It%20was%20an%20easy%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspeechandlastg.wpengine.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Flistening-to-unheard-children-report-final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurvey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Speech%20and%20Language%20UK%2C%20teachers%20believe%20that%20too%20much%20screentime%20is%20causing%20speech%20and%20language%20delays%20in%20young%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20have%20sparked%20a%20debate%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-much-screen-time-is-too-much%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20much%20screen%20time%20is%20too%20much%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20some%20parents%20even%20swearing%20off%20screens%20entirely%20in%20social%20situations.%20But%2C%20for%20me%2C%20a%20screen%20is%20an%20essential%20part%20of%20my%20parenting%20toolkit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EOffering%20screen%20time%20makes%20parenting%20a%20little%20bit%20easier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20go%20out%20for%20lunch%2C%20dinner%2C%20or%20a%20quiet%20drink%20with%20my%20partner%20and%20now%20three-year-old%20daughter%2C%20I%20take%20coloring%20books%2C%20crayons%2C%20Play-Doh%2C%20stickers%2C%20you%20name%20it.%20But%20I%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscreen-free-family-meals-kids-entertainment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20her%20screen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20parent%20brings%20many%20joys%2C%20but%20you%20also%20give%20up%20a%20lot.%20Your%20social%20life%20takes%20a%20back%20seat%2C%20and%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20%26quot%3Bcouple%