%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fgovernment%2Fladakhs-people-wary-of-development-seven-months-after-article-370-read-down%2F%5C%22%3ELadakh%E2%80%99s%20People%20Wary%20of%20%E2%80%98Development%E2%80%99%20Seven%20Months%20After%20Article%20370%20Read-Down%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20reformer%20and%20climate%20change%20activist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fladakhi-innovator-sonam-wangchuk-says-hes-under-house-arrest-police-deny-charge%2Farticle66445976.ece%5C%22%3Ewas%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20following%20a%20five-day%20fast%20in%20support%20of%20protection%20of%20Ladakh%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule.%20The%20Ladakh%20police%20had%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20the%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyed%20Zafar%20Mehdi%2C%20a%20trader%2C%20said%20that%20he%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Turtuk%2C%20the%20last%20village%20on%20the%20border%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20demonstration.%20%E2%80%9CI%20understand%20the%20importance%20of%20issues%20such%20as%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%20statehood%20because%20our%20community%20lives%20in%20front%20of%20the%20enemy.%20I%20fully%20support%20the%20demands%20of%20LAB%20and%20KDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20protesters%20took%20out%20a%20march%20from%20Sengge%20Namgyal%20square%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Leh%20to%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20covering%20a%20distance%20of%20about%20two%20kilometres.%20Throughout%20the%20march%2C%20they%20continued%20to%20chant%20slogans%20while%20displaying%20placards%20advocating%20for%20statehood%2C%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20and%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20demonstration%20was%20held%20in%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20Kargil%20district.%20This%20protest%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20thousands%20of%20people.%20The%20demonstrators%20chanted%20slogans%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlogans%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Nahin%20chalegi%2C%20nahin%20chalegi%2C%20nainsaafi%20nahin%20chalegi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Injustice%20won%E2%80%99t%20work)%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Ladakh%20kay%20tribal%20status%20ko%2C%20nafiz%20karo%20nafiz%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pronounce%20tribal%20status%20for%20Ladakh)%E2%80%99%20echoed%20during%20the%20demonstration%20in%20Kargil%20district%20on%20Saturday.%20Some%20demonstrators%20were%20carrying%20placards%20which%20read%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20demand%20statehood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChering%20Dorjay%2C%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20LBA%20and%20a%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20minister%2C%20said%20that%20the%20outpouring%20of%20support%20for%20the%20shutdown%20call%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20message%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20that%20it%20should%20concede%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20demanding%20anything%20extra-constitutional.%20Tribal%20status%20is%20the%20right%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh.%20The%20Centre%20should%20respect%20our%20sentiments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dorjay%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20Ladakh%20BJP%20in%202020%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%204%2C%20a%20committee%20formed%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20had%20held%20the%20first%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20LAB%20and%20KDA%2C%20without%20any%20significant%20breakthrough.%20While%20the%20committee%20had%20discussed%20%E2%80%9Cconstitutional%20safeguards%E2%80%9D%20for%20Ladakh%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20LAB%20and%20KDA%20have%20stuck%20to%20their%20four%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20on%20February%2019%20