ebruary%2024%2C%202023%20and%20titled%20%E2%80%9CBriefing%20to%20the%20Minister%20of%20Democratic%20Institutions%20on%20Foreign%20Interference%E2%80%9D%2C%20has%20called%20China%20%E2%80%9Cby%20far%20the%20most%20significant%20threat%E2%80%9D%20while%20also%20naming%20India%20as%20a%20foreign%20interference%20threat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outlet%20quoted%20the%20report%20as%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20must%20do%20more%20to%20protect%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20robust%20democratic%20institutions%20and%20processes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20News%20said%20that%20the%20briefing%20report%20was%20released%20to%20it%20under%20the%20Access%20to%20Information%20Act%20as%20a%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20into%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20recent%20elections%20got%20underway%20in%20Ottawa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20wrapped%20up%20its%20first%20set%20of%20hearings%20on%20Friday%20(February%202).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20intelligence%20report%20devoted%20almost%20three%20pages%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20the%20excerpts%20were%20entirely%20redacted%20except%20for%20a%20single%20sentence%20that%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20engages%20in%20FI%20%5Bforeign%20interference%5D%20activities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20the%20only%20country%20identified%20by%20name%20aside%20from%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-probe-panel-to-examine-indias-alleged-role-in-the-last-two-federal-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20foreign%20interference%20commission%20as%20saying%20it%20had%20requested%20the%20Canadian%20government%20to%20provide%20information%20related%20to%20alleged%20interference%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20Canadian%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPursuant%20to%20its%20Terms%20of%20Reference%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Interference%20Commission%20has%20requested%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20collection%20and%20production%20of%20document%20relating%20to%20paragraphs%20clause%20(a)(i)(A)%20and%20(a)(i)(B)%20of%20its%20Terms%20of%20Reference%20include%20information%20and%20documents%20relating%20to%20alleged%20interference%20by%20India%20related%20to%20the%202019%20and%202021%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20briefing%20report%20accessed%20by%20Global%20News%20states%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20extent%20of%20foreign%20interference%20in%20Canada%20is%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%2C%20pervasive%20and%20directed%20against%20all%20levels%20of%20government%20and%20civil%20society%20all%20across%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20has%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20articulated%20strategies%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20raising%20awareness%20and%20briefing%20officials%20and%20politicians%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20to%20these%20efforts%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20that%20all%20government%20agencies%20must%20work%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdetect%2C%20disrupt%20and%20publicise%E2%80%9D%20interference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20responsibility%20to%20counter%20these%20harmful%20activities%20must%20be%20shared%20across%20government%2C%20including%20provincial%20and%20municipal%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20commission%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fdemocratic-institutions%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2Fgovernment-of-canada-launches-public-inquiry-into-foreign-interference.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%20in%20September%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20explicitly%20mentioned%20that%20it%20would%20examine%20interference%20in%20Canadian%20elections%20by%20China%2C%20Russia%20and%20unnamed%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20actors%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20its%20functioning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20according%20to%20last%20month%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%2C%20the%20commission%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20potential%20role%20was%20also%20being%20examined.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20intelligence%20briefing%20report%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20in%20September%20publicly%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20shooting%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20proscribed%20as%20a%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20by%20Indian%20security%20agencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20leader%20Jagmeet%20Singh%2C%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20Trudeau%20government%2C%20had%20written%20to%20the%20commission%20to%20look%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20having%20influenced%20elections%20through%20its%20large%20diaspora.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20on%20its%20part%20had%20denied%20the%20accusation%2C%20with%20both%20countries%20expelling%20a%20diplomat%20each.%20India%20had%20also%20stopped%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20it%20resumed%20after%20about%20a%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20Delhi%20also%20asked%20Canada%20to%20cut%20down%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20so%20that%20there%20is%20parity%2C%20which%20led%20Ottawa%20to%20withdraw%20over%2040%20diplomats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%C2%A0US%20federal%20prosecutors%20announced%20in%20November%20that%20there%20was%20a%20possible%20link%20between%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20and%20the%20foiling%20of%20an%20alleged%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Canadian-American%20Khalistan%20supporter%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Global%20News%2C%20the%20Feburary%202023%20intelligence%20report%20also%20called%20for%20%E2%80%9Cdecisive%20action%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20imposition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconsequences%20on%20perpetrators%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUltimately%2C%20better%20protecting%20Canadian%20democratic%20institutions%20against%20FI%20will%20require%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20take%20decisive%20action%20and%20impose%20consequences%20on%20perpetrators%2C%E2%80%9D%20Global%20News%20quoted%20the%20briefing%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUntil%20FI%20is%20viewed%20as%20constituting%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20Canadian%20democracy%20and%20the%20government%20forcefully%20and%20actively%20responds%2C%20these%20threats%20will%20persist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706963120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19221735%2Fcanadian-flag-1229484_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanada-intelligence-india-foreign-inteference-global-news%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20report%20devoted%20almost%20three%20pages%20to%20India's%20role%2C%20the%20excerpts%20were%20entirely%20redacted%20except%20for%20a%20single%20sentence%20that%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20engages%20in%20FI%20%5Bforeign%20interference%5D%20activities.%E2%80%9D%20India%20is%20the%20only%20country%20identified%20by%20name%20aside%20from%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanada-intelligence-india-foreign-inteference-global-news%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20still%20have%20fears%20about%20marriage%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20being%20divorced%2C%20but%20I'm%20finally%20ready%20for%20a%20commitment%20again.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223861%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Couple%20holding%20hands%2C%20wearing%20wedding%20rings%2C%20on%20their%20wedding%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b937047a3d27148875e056%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMelissa%20Persling%20(not%20pictured)%20got%20divorced%20nearly%2010%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3EAleksandr%20Zubkov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20got%20married%20in%20my%2020s%20and%20things%20didn't%20work%20out.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20been%20nearly%2010%20years%20since%20my%20divorce%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20scared%20of%20marriage%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20I've%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20experience%20and%20I'm%20ready%20for%20a%20serious%20commitment%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%20I%20took%20off%20the%20perfect%20princess%20cut%20diamond%20my%20ex-husband%20proposed%20to%20me%20with%2C%20the%20one%20I%20sold%20when%20I%20couldn't%20make%20rent%20post-divorce%2C%20I%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdivorced-couple-fell-in-love-again-remarry-daughter-documenting-tiktok-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eget%20married%20again%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20finally%20understand%20the%20mistakes%20I%20made%20during%20my%20first%20marriage%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20and%20given%20the%20chance%2C%20I%20know%20I%20can%20make%20a%20second%20marriage%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20flourish%20%E2%80%94%20as%20I%20near%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20admitting%20to%20myself%20that%20I%20want%20to%20get%20married%20again%20is%20scary.%20It's%20terrifying%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20I%20long%20for%20something%20I've%20spent%20nearly%20a%20decade%20avoiding.%20Not%20only%20does%20marriage%20take