m%20Enaz%2FBobby%20Liu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20shed%20body%20fat%2C%20build%20muscle%2C%20and%20get%20stronger%20without%20long%20workouts%20or%20fad%20diets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20personal%20trainer%20who%20helps%20clients%20transform%20their%20fitness%20said%20simple%20routines%20are%20key.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDo%20fewer%20reps%20in%20the%20gym%20and%20flexible%20diet%2C%20and%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20stick%20to%20your%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EForget%20the%20bro%20science%20you%20keep%20seeing%20on%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can%20actually%20work%20smarter%2C%20not%20harder%2C%20in%20the%20gym%20for%20better%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20simple%2C%20sustainable%20routine%20can%20be%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20build%20muscle%20and%20burn%20fat%20with%20less%20time%20and%20effort%2C%20said%20Adam%20Enaz%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%20and%20dietitian%20specializing%20in%20fitness%20transformations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20what%20popular%20fitness%20influencers%20may%20suggest%2C%20severely%20cutting%20calories%2C%20foregoing%20carbs%2C%20and%20exhausting%20yourself%20on%20the%20treadmill%20isn't%20the%20best%20way%20to%20get%20ripped%2C%20according%20to%20Enaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20bro%20science%20in%20the%20fitness%20community%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20men%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20this%20idea%20that%20to%20get%20fit%20you%20need%20to%20run%20loads%20and%20eat%20low%20carb.%20It's%20the%20opposite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnaz%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkout-less-for-maximum-muscle-building-gains-trainer-advice-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20few%20hours%20of%20lifting%20weights%20per%20week%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20some%20basic%20nutrition%20know-how%20is%20all%20you%20need%20to%20create%20a%20lasting%20routine%20to%20shed%20body%20fat%20and%20pack%20on%20lean%20muscle%20%E2%80%94%20no%20fad%20diets%20or%20back-breaking%20workout%20trends%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStop%20doing%20endless%20cardio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20common%20issues%20that%20can%20prevent%20people%20from%20reaching%20their%20aesthetic%20goals%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-lifting-better-than-cardio-body-builder-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcessive%20cardio%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20burn%20body%20fat%2C%20according%20to%20Enaz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20do%20cardio%20you%20lose%20fat%20and%20become%20slim%20but%20you%20don't%20get%20toned%20or%20get%20an%20aesthetic%20appearance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-workout-viral-trend-not-worth-effort-try-other-exercises-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToo%20much%20cardio%20can%20be%20a%20waste%20of%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20want%20to%20build%20muscle.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-zone-2-cardio-exercise-training-benefits-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaerobic%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20important%20for%20overall%20health%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20shorter%20workouts%20with%20weight%20training%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20more%20defined%20muscles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-better-cardio-burning-fat-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20lifting%20weights%20is%20key%20to%20prompting%20muscle%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLifting%20weights%20made%20me%20more%20confident%2C%20stronger%2C%20and%20helped%20me%20get%20the%20appearance%20I%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20Enaz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20concept%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprogressive-overload-fitness-meaning-and-how-to-do-it-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprogressive%20overload%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20key%20to%20getting%20great%20results%20lifting%20weights%2C%20Enaz%20said.%20What%20it%20means%20is%20that%20you%20need%20to%20continually%20challenge%20the%20muscles%20over%20time%20by%20lifting%20gradually%20heavier%20weights%2C%20or%20with%20more%20reps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20need%20to%20hit%20every%20muscle%20group%20from%20every%20angle%20to%20make%20gains.%20One%20client%20working%20with%20Enaz%20saw%20more%20defined%20muscles%20with%20four%20hours%20of%20weekly%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20smashing%20their%20chest%20and%20biceps%2C%20doing%20three%20to%20four%20exercises%20in%20a%20session%20thinking%20it%20will%20cause%20muscle%20growth%2C%20but%20you'll%20reach%20a%20plateau%2C%26quot%3B%20Enaz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F02640414.2016.1210197%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20you%20can%20get%2080%25%20of%20potential%20muscle%20gains%20with%20between%20five%20to%20nine%20sets%20a%20week%20per%20muscle%20group%20%E2%80%94%20after%20that%2C%20additional%20sets%20lead%20to%20diminishing%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20a%20man's%20arms%20and%20legs%20as%20he%20prepares%20to%20do%20a%20heavy%20deadlift%20exercise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd14b36fcb546d2d4b9a12%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWeighted%20exercises%20like%20deadlifts%20offer%20a%20lot%20of%20benefits%20for%20a%20short%20time%20in%20the%20gym%2C%20helping%20to%20build%20muscle%20and%20work%20your%20whole%20body%20at%20once.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStick%20to%20simple%20exercises%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEnaz%20coaches%20in-person%20sessions%20based%20in%20London%2C%20but%20also%20helps%20clients%20worldwide%20with%20virtual%20sessions.%20He%20said%20exercises%20with%20dumbbells%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-use-gym-machines-to-build-muscle-for-beginners-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egym%20machines%20like%20the%20leg%20press%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20great%20for%20building%20muscle%20for%20fitness%20beginners%2C%20since%20they%20don't%20require%20complicated%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstop-overcomplicating-workouts-personal-trainers-reduce-injury-risk-get-results-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20overcomplicate%20your%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20either%2C%20since%20classic%20compound%20movements%20like%20deadlifts%2C%20shoulder%20presses%2C%20and%20the%20like%20can%20work%20multiple%20muscle%20groups%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20cut%20carbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELow-carb%20diets%20have%20become%20a%20popular%20weight-loss%20strategy%2C%20but%20they%20may%20not%20be%20your%20best%20bet%20for%20building%20strength%20and%20muscle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarbohydrates%20are%20a%20crucial%20source%20of%20energy%2C%20especially%20for%20providing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-low-carb-diet-bad-high-intensity-exercise-muscle-loss-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20fuel%20during%20intense%20exercises%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dietitians%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnaz%20said%20a%20high-carb%20diet%20with%20weight%20lifting%20can%20be%20a%20better%20strategy%20for%20creating%20a%20lean%2C%20muscular%20physique.%20One%20of%20his%20clients%2C%2045-year-old%20Bobby%20Liu%2C%20achieved%20better%20muscle%20definition%2C%20increased%20his%20strength%2C%20and%20reduced%20his%20belly%20fat%20by%20eating%20a%20flexible%2C%20high-carb%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEat%20enough%20food%2C%20especially%20protein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20working%20hard%20in%20the%20gym%20but%20not%20seeing%20results%2C%20you%20might%20not%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-not-eating-enough-to-build-muscle-sports-dietitian-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20enough%20to%20build%20muscle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20a%20calorie%20deficit%20is%20important%20for%20burning%20fat%2C%20undereating%20by%20too%20much%20can%20cause%20you%20to%20lose%20muscle%20mass%20instead%20of%20fat.%20Enaz%20said%20that's%20why%20people%20don't%20see%20results%20if%20they%20cut%20calories%20severely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20you%20also%20don't%20need%20to%20overdo%20it%20if%20you're%20trying%20to%20build%20muscle%20mass%20%E2%80%94%20an%20extra%20hundred%20calories%20a%20day%20can%20be%20a%20good%20start%2C%20Enaz%20said.%20Eating%20more%20won't%20necessarily%20build%20muscle%20tissue%20any%20quicker%2C%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20fat%20gain%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20men%20are%20trying%20to%20gain%20muscle%2C%20they%20think%20they%20need%20to%20eat%20as%20many%20calories%20as%20they%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Enaz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStay%20consistent%20and%20be%20patient%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrograms%20that%20promise%20amazing%20results%20at%20lightning%20speed%20likely%20aren't%20sustainable%2C%20and%20you're%20better%20off%20taking%20a%20slow%20and%20steady%20approach%20to%20see%20real%2C%20lasting%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20things%20quick%2C%20especially%20when%20everyone%20has%20a%20six-pack%20on%20Instagram%20and%20people%20are%20photoshopped.%20It%20makes%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20need%20to%20look%20like%20that%20right%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnaz%20said%20his%20approach%20to%20fitness%20often%20surprises%20clients%20who%20expect%20a%20more%20complicated%20secret%20to%20achieving%20their%20goals.%20But%20it's%20not%20a%20unique%20exercise%20or%20diet%20that%20leads%20to%20gains%2C%20it's%20mastering%20the%20basics%20and%20sticking%20to%20them%20over%20time%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20people%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%20it's%20that%20they're%20irregular.%20They%20do%20it%20for%20a%20week%2C%20and%20then%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Enaz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-fat-build-muscle-workouts-diet-personal-trainer-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706962442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd143443bb77284ba30689%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-fat-build-muscle-workouts-diet-personal-trainer-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doing%20less%20with%20your%20workouts%20and%20diet%20can%20lead%20to%20better%20results%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%20said.%20Focus%20on%20basics%20like%20eating%20protein%20and%20lifting%20weights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-fat-build-muscle-workouts-diet-personal-trainer-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Goodluck%20Q3%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20grows%2072%25%20to%20Rs%2032%20crore%2C%20income%20up%2024%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706962313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-02%2F19%2Ffull%2F1676817940-8267.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fgoodluck-q3-results-net-profit-grows-72-to-rs-32-crore-income-up-24-124020300780_