20mark%20the%2070th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20Two%20on%20September%203%2C%202015%2C%20in%20Beijing%2C%20China.%3Cp%3EAndy%20Wong%20-%20Pool%20%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20have%20seekers%20and%20sophisticated%20guidance%20systems%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20find%20a%20ship%20mid-flight%20and%20home%20in%20on%20it%2C%20Clark%20said.%20The%20Houthi%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20don't%20appear%20to%20have%20these%20same%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20be%20launched%20at%20a%20geographic%20point%20and%20hope%20that%20they%20hit%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unlike%20the%20Houthis%2C%20the%20Chinese%20military%20also%20has%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20sensors%20available%20that%20they%20can%20use%20to%20direct%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20strikes%2C%20said%20Shaan%20Shaikh%2C%20a%20fellow%20with%20the%20Missile%20Defense%20Project%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20think%20tank.%20These%20capabilities%20include%20various%20platforms%20like%20ground-based%20radar%20systems%2C%20ships%2C%20maritime%20drones%2C%20and%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20all%20of%20these%20different%20sensors%20that%20are%20available%20to%20China%20to%20help%20complete%20that%20kill%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaikh%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20In%20a%20conflict%2C%20China's%20anti-ship%20ballistic%20missiles%20also%20might%20also%20require%20US%20Navy%20ships%20to%20expend%20more%20advanced%20interceptors%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20the%20threat%20environment%20in%20the%20Pacific%20may%20be%20more%20sophisticated%20and%20challenging%20than%20it%20is%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20experts%20say%20the%20crews%20aboard%20American%20warships%20%E2%80%94%20relentlessly%20tasked%20with%20shooting%20down%20Houthi%20anti-ship%20ballist