%2C%20although%20not%20made%20public%20in%20full%2C%20is%20thought%20to%20contain%20conditions%20for%20small-scale%20prisoner%20releases%2C%20contingent%20on%20hostages%20being%20freed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20clear%20when%20or%20if%20Hamas%20will%20give%20a%20clearer%20answer%20on%20the%20proposal%20or%20make%20a%20counterproposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20says%20Algerian%20security%20council%20cease-fire%20resolution%20jeopardizes%20truce%20talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20said%20Friday%20that%20an%20Algerian%20draft%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolution%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcease-fire-truce-armistice-whats-the-difference%2Fa-67243219%5C%22%3Ecalling%20for%20an%20immediate%20cease-fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Gaza%20could%20jeopardize%20the%20talks%20on%20a%20possible%20halt%20in%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20draft%20resolution%20could%20put%20sensitive%20negotiations%20in%20jeopardy%20%E2%80%94%20derailing%20the%20exhaustive%2C%20ongoing%20diplomatic%20efforts%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20and%20secure%20an%20extended%20pause%20that%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20aid%20workers%20so%20desperately%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20Linda%20Thomas-Greenfield%2C%20the%20US%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%2C%C2%A0told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20emerged%20this%20week%20that%20Algeria%20submitted%20the%20draft%20resolution%20to%20the%20Security%20Council%20on%20Wednesday.%20Whether%20it%20will%20come%20to%20a%20vote%20or%20a%20debate%20is%20not%20clear%3B%20it%20already%20appears%20unlikely%20that%20it%20would%20pass%2C%20given%20the%20need%20to%20avoid%20a%20US%20veto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20accepted%20and%20implemented%2C%20this%20proposal%20would%20move%20all%20parties%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20creating%20the%20conditions%20for%20a%20sustainable%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Thomas-Greenfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20argued%20it%20was%20the%20Security%20Council%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cobligation%20to%20ensure%20that%20any%20action%20we%20take%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20increases%20pressure%20on%20Hamas%20to%20accept%20this%20proposal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cstrong%3EWestern%20foreign%20ministers%20still%C2%A0trying%20to%20mediate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20push%20for%20a%20period%20of%20reduced%20fighting%2C%20after%20the%20collapse%20of%C2%A0a%20one-week%20truce%20punctuated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-and-hamas-hostage-deal-what-do-we-know%2Fa-67518562%5C%22%3Eprisoner%20swaps%20last%20November%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20coincides%20with%20continued%20intensive%20diplomatic%20efforts%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20Foreign%20Secretary%20David%20Cameron%20was%20in%20Beirut%20on%20Friday%2C%20where%20he%20seemed%20to%20encourage%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20engage%20on%20the%20question%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fis-palestine-considered-a-state%2Fa-67310981%5C%22%3Efuture%20Palestinian%20state%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECameron%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20aired%20by%20Lebanese%20broadcaster%20LBCI%20that%20despite%20some%20of%20his%20recent%20comments%2C%20Netanyahu%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20ruled%20out%20comprehensively%20a%20two-state%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20message%20to%20him%20was%20start%20talking%20about%20the%20things%20that%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20could%20be%20rather%20than%20the%20things%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Cameron.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20would%20come%20a%20time%20when%20British%20policy%20would%20look%20to%20recognize%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20including%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Cameron.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20needs%20to%20get%20going.%20But%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20Foreign%20Minister%20Stephane%20Sejourne%20is%20also%20expected%20in%20the%20region%C2%A0on%20Saturday%2C%20first%20in%20Israel.%20And%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20will%20again%20tour%20the%20region%20from%20February%204%20to%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20fighters%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20and%20took%20more%20than%20200%20others%20hostage%C2%A0during%20terror%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisraeli-bombardment-recurring-nightmare-for-gaza-residents%2Fa-67081716%5C%22%3EIsrael%20has%20responded%20with%20an%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Hamas-run%20Health%20Ministry%20says%20has%20killed%C2%A027%2C131%20people%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20ministry%2C%20which%C2%A0does%20not%20distinguish%20between%20civilian%20and%20combatant%20casualties%2C%20said%C2%A0on%20Friday%20that%20112%20people%20had%20died%20in%20the%20previous%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhamas-considers-gaza-truce-proposal-endorsed-by-israel%2Fa-68159857%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706951968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08150335%2Fimage560x340cropped.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhamas-considers-gaza-truce-proposal-endorsed-by-israel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20officials%20have%20said%20leaders%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20in%20Cairo%20for%20talks%2C%20were%20weighing%20a%20proposal%20for%20a%20longer-term%20truce%20that%20has%20Israeli%20support.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%