bly%20and%20what%20was%20shared%20through%20RTI%20replies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EContext%20on%20rules%20for%20%E2%80%98official%20trips%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20December%2C%20after%20a%20video%20clip%20of%20the%20entire%20Karnataka%20cabinet%20chartering%20a%20flight%20to%20New%20Delhi%20had%20gone%20viral%2C%20the%20BJP%20accused%20the%20Congress-led%20government%20of%20wasting%20taxpayers%E2%80%99%20money%20on%20%E2%80%9Cluxury%20lifestyles%E2%80%9D%20while%20the%20state%20grappled%20with%20a%20severe%20drought.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-cm-ministers-visit-to-delhi-in-private-jet-sparks-political-row-101703271974291.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBengaluru%253A%2520A%2520viral%2520video%2520of%2Cthe%2520state%2520grappled%2520with%2520a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20had%20responded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20stating%20that%20the%20leaders%20were%20returning%20from%20New%20Delhi%20after%20meeting%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20over%20release%20of%20funds%20for%20drought%20relief%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20official%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20amended%20rules%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Frules-amended-for-dy-cms-to-use-government-aircraft%2Farticleshow%2F103700691.cms%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Maharashtra%2520government%2520has%2520amended%2Cministers%2520apart%2520from%2520the%2520CM.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Euse%20of%20state-owned%20aircraft%20and%20helicopters%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20give%20easier%20access%20to%20the%20governor%20and%20the%20two%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20but%20stipulated%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20those%20uses%20also%20had%20to%20be%20official%20work.%20The%20tweaking%20of%20that%20government%E2%80%99s%20rules%20came%20after%20the%20outgoing%20governor%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fdispatches%2Fmaharashtra-governor-forced-to-take-a-commercial-plane-to-dehradun-from-mumbai-airport-after-he-was-refused-the-use-of-the-states-plane-by-the-government%2Farticle33820636.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagat%20Singh%20Koshiari%20was%20famously%20refused%20permission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20to%20use%20the%20official%20aircraft%20to%20fly%20to%20Dehradun%20in%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%2026%2C%202021%2C%20the%20Assam%20cabinet%20had%20also%20decided%20to%20hire%20helicopters%20and%20chartered%20aircraft%20for%20the%20governor%2C%20chief%20minister%2C%20ministers%20and%20senior%20government%20officials%20but%20noted%20that%20they%20would%20be%20strictly%20for%20official%20visits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20also%20noteworthy%20is%20that%20as%20per%20the%20RTI%20replies%2C%20between%20May%2010%2C%202021%20till%20the%20time%20when%20the%20information%20was%20furnished%20in%20September%202023%2C%20the%20state%20exchequer%20bore%20a%20staggering%20Rs%2045%2C62%2C05%2C755%20to%20meet%20the%20supply%20of%20helicopters%20and%20chartered%20flights%20to%20ferry%20top%20state%20dignitaries.%20The%20maximum%20number%20of%20flights%20were%20undertaken%20by%20CM%20Sarma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20between%20May%2020%2C%202021%20and%20July%2018%2C%202021%2C%20all%20such%20flights%20cost%20the%20Assam%20government%20Rs%204%2C46%2C09836%2C%20of%20which%20Rs%203%2C30%2C03834%20was%20only%20for%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20journeys.%20Since%20the%20information%20provided%20by%20his%20government%20is%20partial%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20compute%20the%20total%20expenditure%20on%20his%20chartered%20flights.%20However%2C%20what%20can%20be%20said%20from%20the%20information%20provided%20is%20that%20Sarma%20used%20such%20chartered%20flights%20for%20240%20days%2C%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years.%20He%20took%20most%20of%20those%20flights%20to%20travel%20from%20Guwahati%20to%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20the%20bills%20provided%20with%20the%20RTI%20replies%20show%20that%20chartered%20flights%20or%20helicopters%20hired%20from%20a%20private%20player%20on%20the%20Guwahati-Delhi%20route%20had%20cost%20the%20state%20government%20between%20Rs%202%2C25%2C000%20and%20Rs.%204%2C15%2C000%20per%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20aircraft%20it%20picked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20the%20state%20government%20hired%20a%20flight%20from%20Guwahati%20to%20Delhi%20at%20the%20rate%20of%20Rs%204%2C15%2C000%20per%20hour%20between%20September%2020%20and%2021%2C%202021%2C%20the%20bill%20would%20come%20to%20Rs%2033%2C10%2C606%2C%20including%2018%25%20GST%20and%20ground-handling%2C%20watch%20extension%2C%20crew%20and%20belt%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20such%20bill%20of%20a%20chartered%20flight%20within%20Assam%2C%20on%20the%20Guwahati-to-Haflong%20circuit%2C%20showed%20cost%20Rs%2024%2C23%2C750%2C%20including%2018%25%20GST%20and%20other%20related%20charges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECosts%20to%20debt-ridden%20Assam%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20government%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20reply%20has%20shown%20that%20it%20had%20spent%20crores%20to%20meet%20the%20chartered%20flight%20requirements%20for%20top%20leaders%20in%20Assam%2C%20including%20chief%20minister%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20unofficial%20engagements%2C%20like%20political%20campaigning%2C%20party%20meetings%20and%20other%20social%20obligations%2C%20like%20attending%20wedding%20parties.%20Meanwhile%2C%20official%20data%20highlights%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20precarious%20financial%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20data%20uploaded%20online%20in%20December%2C%20till%20the%20Tarun%20Gogoi-led%20Congress%20government%20held%20office%2C%20the%20Assam%20government%20had%20an%20outstanding%20loan%20of%20Rs%2041%2C963%20crores.%20The%20amount%20has%20ballooned%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years%20of%20BJP%20rule%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20state.%20As%20of%20the%20financial%20year%202022-23%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20financial%20liabilities%20stood%20at%20almost%20three%20times%20that%20%E2%80%93%20at%20a%20whopping%20Rs%201%2C26%2C281.4%20crores.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20this%20rate%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20the%20total%20outstanding%20financial%20liabilities%20of%20Assam%20are%20expected%20to%20rise%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.rbi.org.in%2FScripts%2FPublicationsView.aspx%3Fid%3D22284%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0further%20to%20Rs%20150%2C900%20crores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706934659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03085026%2FUntitled-design-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-public-money-helicopter-chartered-flights-bjp-party-wedding%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarma%2C%20who%20moved%20to%20the%20BJP%20only%20in%202015%20and%20rose%20quickly%20to%20an%20important%20position%2C%20is%20often%20out%20of%20Assam%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20party.%20It%20turns%20out%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20are%20paying%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-public-money-helicopter-chartered-flights-bjp-party-wedding%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20member%20of%20Parliamen