0finance%20minister%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20of%20the%20lost%20decade%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20that%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20ideological%20underpinnings%20in%20her%20budget%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20emphasised%20the%20shift%20from%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearlier%20approach%20of%20tackling%20poverty%20through%20entitlements%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20new%20mantra%20of%20%E2%80%9Cempowering%20the%20poor%E2%80%9D.%20In%20effect%2C%20she%20denounced%20the%20understanding%20where%20the%20citizenry%20was%20entitled%20to%20social%20welfare%20%E2%80%93%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20pensions%20%E2%80%93%20and%20could%20demand%20it%20from%20the%20state%20as%20a%20right.%20Instead%2C%20she%20spoke%20of%20having%20supplanted%20this%20with%20a%20new%20perspective%20that%20sees%20citizens%20as%20mere%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20recipients%20of%20the%20ruler%E2%80%99s%20benevolence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20Sitharaman%20unveiled%20the%20new%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98social%20justice%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%20as%20delivery%20of%20benefits%20and%20services.%20%E2%80%9CPreviously%2C%20social%20justice%20was%20mostly%20a%20political%20slogan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20her%20speech.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20our%20government%2C%20social%20justice%20is%20an%20effective%20and%20necessary%20governance%20model%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20implying%20the%20importance%20of%20reaching%20all%20eligible%20beneficiaries%20through%20what%20she%20refers%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Csaturation%20approach%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20one%E2%80%99s%20social%20position%20continues%20to%20determine%20one%E2%80%99s%20opportunities%2C%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20political%20clout%2C%20can%20we%20afford%20to%20reduce%20social%20justice%20to%20mere%20service%20delivery%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constitution%20enjoins%20upon%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20justice%20within%20%E2%80%98social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%E2%80%99%20realms.%20But%20the%20BJP%20wishes%20to%20reduce%20it%20to%20only%20benefit%20delivery%20as%20is%20evident%20in%20its%20resistance%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20socio-economic%20caste%20census.%20Such%20a%20census%20will%20enable%20better%20policies%20to%20ensure%20political%20and%20institutional%20inclusion%20of%20the%20marginalised%20community.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20budget%20allocation%20for%20%E2%80%98Census%20Survey%20and%20Statistics%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%2Fdoc%2Feb%2Fallsbe.pdf%5C%22%3Ecut%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20government%20has%20no%20intention%20to%20undertake%20a%20census%20any%20time%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20there%20has%20been%20concerted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-bjp-rsss-quest-for-the-acceptable-muslim%5C%22%3Eeffort%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20to%20claim%20that%20Muslims%20have%20been%20a%20major%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20the%20government%20has%20not%20discriminated%20among%20its%20%3Cem%3Elabharthis%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20her%20budget%20speech%2C%20Sitharaman%20calls%20this%20%E2%80%9Csecularism%20in%20action%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERSS%E2%80%99s%20mouthpiece%20calls%20this%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forganiser.org%2F2023%2F08%2F06%2F188036%2Fopinion%2Ffrom-appeasement-to-empowerment-muslim-welfare-under-modi-government%2F%5C%22%3Eshift%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%20to%20empowerment%E2%80%9D.%20But%20can%20one%20strip%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fpeople-with-beards-caps-will-be-beaten-up-if-seen-near-hindu-sites-jharkhand-bjp-mla%5C%22%3Ecommunity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjunagadh-muslims-targeted-flogged-after-protest-over-possible-dargah-demolition%5C%22%3Eof%20i