C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERajiv%20worked%20on%2020%20prototypes%20before%20making%20the%20final%20product%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20his%20younger%20years%2C%20Rajiv%20has%20been%20creating%20various%20products.%20Amidst%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20he%20constructed%20a%20comfortable%20PPE%20kit%20suitable%20for%20extended%20wear.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%2C%20he%20also%20developed%20over%2050%20wheelchairs%20for%20injured%20or%20paralysed%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20practised%20carpentry%20till%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20adept%20at%20tools%20and%20electrical%20design%20due%20to%20my%20course%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20found%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20air%20fresheners%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20anything%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etruly%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20his%20passion%20for%20creation%20pushed%20him%20to%20build%20one%20using%20natural%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20poisonous%20chemicals%20in%20air%20fresheners.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20read%20the%20ingredient%20list%20behind%20any%20air%20freshener.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20safe%20for%20children%20(mentioned%20in%20the%20packaging)%20and%20animals%20to%20inhale.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20freshener%20which%20was%20safe%20for%20the%20environment%20as%20well%20as%20humans%20and%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Rajiv%20focused%20on%20creating%20natural%20fragrances%20using%20flower%20waste.%20He%20collected%20jasmine%20and%20roses%20from%20a%20nearby%20temple%2C%20air-dried%20the%20petals%2C%20ground%20them%20int